                                div.meta Mitchell Gu, Jiahao Li, Travis Libsack, Joe Huang
                                div.description
                                  | A framework for 3D sketching that allows a user to use a "pen and paper" 
                                  | interface to create 3D models. We triangulate the position using ultrasonic 
                                  | rangefinder data from three counterweight heights sent from an Intel Edison. 
                                  | Our 3D visualization client allows users to draw polygons, 3D surfaces, and 
                                  | smooth curves depending on button input from the sketching pen.

                      h3 Remaining Top Ten (Alphabetical Order)

